{"tid":127227,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港首架免費WiFi小巴","createTime":"2017-02-20T03:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T09:32:31.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"050d3ea1e69a764b61445a80210784a340981084","tid":127227,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:01:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/tech/art/20170214/19927414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftech%2Fart%2F20170214%2F19927414&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=9e315041\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftech%2Fart%2F20170214%2F19927414&h=0ed41ad0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/tech/art/20170214/19927414</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170214/large/801ss01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170214%2Flarge%2F801ss01.jpg&h=000604a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現今社會人人機不離手，網絡數據計劃多多都不夠用，如果坐公共交通工具時有免費WiFi相信會是大家的喜訊。本港就即將出現第一輛有免費WiFi的小巴了！記者更登上了這小巴，一試其網絡速度！<br />\n<br />\n要用此免費WiFi很簡單，只要先掃瞄QR code，再輸入電郵地址就可以啟用，記者亦用了通訊事務管理局的App OFCA測試速度，得出下載每秒7.05mb，上載每秒3.8mb，不過數字難以表達實際使用感覺，所以記者又測試看一條完整的動新聞，一開頭用了不少處理時間，但到播放動新聞時，畫面大致暢順，不會見到不斷緩衝等等，而且服務是免費，也不能強求太多吧。<br />\n<br />\n不過每人每日只限10分鐘免費試用，而初步有免費WiFi的小巴路線就只有三條，分別是從九龍塘出發的25M、25M(S)，及新蒲崗出發的85號小巴，一共36輛車。使用時段內，除了WiFi之外亦有國際長途電話服務，不知又能否方便到你呢？"},{"pid":"bb42144c6fff1525084d7c85ec6c53f2f02045af","tid":127227,"uid":72409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:03:45.000Z","msg":"完<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"799053b2d42fe0c312d6c528e08a06d255629f2d","tid":127227,"uid":42419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:04:23.000Z","msg":"綠van多數搭一陣就落車 連得wifi嚟都要落車啦"},{